CREATE TABLE recycling_centers (
  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  name VARCHAR(255),
  location VARCHAR(255),
  capacity INT,
  waste_type VARCHAR(50)
)

  id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  collection_date DATE,
  weight DECIMAL(10,2),
  center_id INT,
  FOREIGN KEY (center_id) REFERENCES recycling_centers(id)
)

)

  value DECIMAL(10,2)
)

)
